snippet.title: Dust: An Elysian Tail - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Become the storm that changes the world in Dust: An Elysian Tail--the critically-acclaimed, hand-animated epic. Join the warrior, Dust, along with the mythical Blade of Ahrah and its colorful sword-guardian, Fidget. Together, your action-packed journey will take you across a dangerous, beautiful world gripped by unending war.

Dust: An Elysian Tail for Nintendo Switch is available now! https://goo.gl/A57mpn
